article_metadata.description:
With today&rsquo;s emphasis on population health strategies to address &ldquo;upstream&rdquo; factors affecting health care, such as
housing and nutrition deficiencies, there is growing interest in the potential role of hospitals to be effective leaders
in tackling upstream factors that influence health, social and economic wellbeing.&nbsp;

